Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People put your guns up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First I'll run dat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:27.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西(にし)）ハァハァ ハァハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Run around and shoot them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brand new sound, yes still survival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the sound boy, live in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Intelligence, strength, and luck are swirling, flow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My swelled mind is candid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One punch to Banner in Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤(かとう)）いちばん帰りたいの…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An easy knockout, bam bam bam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One time for your mind, live through this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺なんだよね\N（計）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It haunts me, the pain of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the noble god are borrowed things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When the seed that's sown flowers, whose is it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Live and fire the arrow of faith, more more more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no peace where you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stand up, don't give up the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, yes, this instant, die die die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Big shooter, living fast, blazing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat you up, cut it open, break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shot shooter, he lived fast, crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjust your sights at point-blank range, break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Big shooter, living fast, blazing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat you up, cut it open, break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shot shooter, he lived fast, crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjust your sights at point-blank range, break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of a brand new day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A day filled with hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your heart to happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And look up at the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:02:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to the voice on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And fill your lungs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With the fragrant air
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Two! Three! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He Can't Shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who wants\Nto go home the most is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本(きしもと)）加藤君 ムリよ！ 戻って！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna make it! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（北条(ほうじょう)）あいつ マジかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuckin' moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（欣二(きんじ)）\Nバカが！ てめえも死んじまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, you can go die too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんてこと言うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？ やっちまうぞ この巨乳が！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss Melons, don't make\Nme come over there and bang ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurono!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄野(くろの)君 なんとかしてよ！ 加藤君を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something! You've gotta help Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,NISHI!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）やめろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:08.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）西ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma! My ears hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太(りょうた)）おばあちゃん お耳痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カヨ）よしよし 大丈夫かい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you old ass, shut him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（北条）\Nばばあ いいかげんにしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But he says his ears are hurting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カヨ）でも この子 耳が痛いって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（北条）何でもねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鉄男(てつお)）それよりよ\Nあのバカ 死んだ …のか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that.\NThere, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that.\NOh you poor thing. Alright now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you poor thing. Alright now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that idiot...\NOh you poor thing. Alright now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?\NThere, there. Easy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちだっていいさ そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if he is or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉(はるや)）ざまあみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）間に合わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）プハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西！\N（岸本・計）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを殺して…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't give up easily, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ しぶといねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（欣二）\N死んじゃえば良かったのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it woulda been better if he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裕三(ゆうぞう)君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,SOMEBODY PLEASE KILL HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:15.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か こいつを殺してくれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all can go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:21.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）\N全員 帰れる！　俺も無傷で！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I can get back safe too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）早く！\N（せきこみ）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く！\N（加藤）殺す？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鈴木星人）裕三君？\N（エネルギーの上昇音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:40.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）銃で… 銃で撃て！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤君 来るよ！ 逃げて 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming! Get out of there! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤 逃げろ！\Nお前 狙われてんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そうはいかない！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:59.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西を… 西を助けないと！\N（計）な… 何言ってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to save Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎！ だったら早く撃て！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you hurry up and shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうよ　逃げないんなら撃って！\Nそうじゃないと死んじゃうってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta shoot him\Nif you're not going to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you're going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本）撃って！ 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何してるのよ？ 加藤君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岸本 あいつ 撃てねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't shoot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But... We don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも\Nそんなこと言ってる場合じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it, and so does Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:45.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）そんなことは分かってるよ\Nあいつだって よ～く分かってるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど あいつは撃てない\Nそういうヤツなんだよ 昔から
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how Kato is...\Nand how he's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺だって まだ撃ったことない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never shot anyone myself,\Nbut maybe one day I'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど いつかは撃つかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:03.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど あいつは撃たない ずっと\N（岸本）そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kato, he won't fire that gun.\NHe'll never do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）俺…\N計算高いヤなヤツに見えたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that sounded\Ntoo cold and calculating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to talk trash about Kato\Njust because I want to do her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:12.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に 岸本とヤリたいから\N加藤の悪口言ったわけじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 悪口じゃねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's not like I said\Nanything bad about him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to tell her is that\NKato is too kind a person to shoot anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:18.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 加藤は優しいヤツだって\N言いたかっただけで…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤 ムリだ　お前 撃てない！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up... You just can't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本）加藤君 助けなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta help Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, guys! If we don't hurry, Kato will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 早くしないと加藤君が…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン！ なんで？\N（春哉）自分で行け バ～カ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Why should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go do it yourself, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, fuck it! What the hell\Nare we doing here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アア… なんか どうでもいいや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで\Nこんな所にいるんだ？ 俺たち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉）帰ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえもな\N俺 殴ってる暇があったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you got time to beat me up, why don't\Nyou go help that fuckin' leader? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのムカつくリーダー助けてやれや\Nああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鉄男）クッ…\N（岸本）ちょ… ちょっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:57.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（欣二）ああ ラーメン ラーメン\N（春哉）歯ぁ痛(いて)えや ちくしょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, my mouth hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亮太\Nおばあちゃんたちも行こうかね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go too, Ryota?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody... Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本）誰か お願い！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジ？ こっちに振るのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to look to me for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ま…\N（岸本）私が行く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna help Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤君 助けたいし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hate hearing you people say I'll die\Nunless I rely on someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かに頼らないと死んじゃうなんて\N言われたのも悔しいし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行く\N（計）待って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が… 行くよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'II...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど… どうすればいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ 脅しに使うんなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can use this to keep him at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動きも牽制(けんせい)できるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フゥ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）おい！ 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か… 聞こえない…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... hear anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軽い…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうまで 行けるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I make back over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）動きを…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）止めろ\N（加藤）はぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… 西！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's... Where's the gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゅ… 銃は？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裕三君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤 …君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:32.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤！\N（岸本）加藤君？ 加藤君！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... hell just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 どうなっちまったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:50.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…\N（岸本）加藤君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet they're all dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:02.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつら 今ごろ\Nみんなして死んでたりしてな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I give a shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:06.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おら 知らねえ\Nああ それよりラーメンな ラーメン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want right now is some ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah... You wanna\Nsee a dentist first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ\Nお前は歯医者が先か ヘヘッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉）\Nチッ… こんな時間に開いてねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dentist\Nwould be open this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:17.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）\Nおばあちゃん おなかすいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだね 亮太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we call your mother\Nand have her pick us up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:24.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今から お母さんに電話して\N車で迎えに来てもらおうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have her pick up a hamburger\Nand you can eat it in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,途中で\Nハンバーガー買ってきてもらおうね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしたら\N車の中で食べればいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亮太）うん それなら いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of a brand new day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...\NIt's the beginning of a brand new day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変だね　壊れてるのかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's broken?\NIt's the beginning of a brand new day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's broken?\NA day filled with hope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A day filled with hope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your heart to happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid!\NOpen your heart to happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:54.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（欣二）おい ガキ\Nなに見てやがんだ？ ああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you looking at, huh? Jeez...\NOpen your heart to happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you looking at, huh? Jeez...\NAnd look up at the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…たく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And look up at the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got some smokes?\NAnd look up at the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい よう タバコ持ってねえか？\N（春哉）ねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And look up at the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Dropped 'em somewhere...\NAnd look up at the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Dropped 'em somewhere...\NListen to the voice on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっかに落とした\N（欣二）マジかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?\NListen to the voice on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And fill your lungs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well... Time for ramen!\NAnd fill your lungs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃあねえな　ラーメン ラーメン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well... Time for ramen!\NWith the fragrant air
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With the fragrant air
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Two! Three! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go.\NOne! Two! Three! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（欣二）おい 早く行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Two! Three! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おばあちゃん あのおにいちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's head is... gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頭 なくなっちゃった…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亮太ったら もう… ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo... Ryota! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,りょ… 亮太 出るのよ！\N（亮太）痛い 痛いよ おばあちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! You're hurting me, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）大丈夫か？ 加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）あ… ああ なんとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く… 玄野君 どうしよう？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurono...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come! Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）\N近づかないほうがいい　近づくな！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど… どうなってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グエッ！ グエッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:39.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本）変な におい…\N（計）キ… キモイ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）これから どうすんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:45.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え… え～っと ネギ星人のとき…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when we fought the Green onion Alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he used this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か これ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）\N大丈夫　でかいけど鳥だ 鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is big,\Nbut it's just a bird. Only a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）\Nどうなってる？ 計ちゃん 何した？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that made it shoot up in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）上に送ったらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）終わった…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西… 西は？ 西！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）おい 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:11.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わったぞ\Nおい 聞こえないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛え…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛え… ウウッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,His ears are bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:21.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本）耳から血が出てる\N（計）鼓膜やられたんじゃねえの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess his eardrums burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back\Nto that room now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから\Nまた部屋に戻るんだよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）あっ そういや おかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time the transporting\Nstarted right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前のときは\Nすぐ 送るやつ始まってたけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして移動 始まらないの？\N（計）変だな どうしてだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't it transporting us back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ終わってねえんじゃねえのか？\N（計）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんで？\N（岸本）そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:50.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）まだいるんじゃねえのか？\Nネギ星人のときみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how it happened\Nwith the Green onion Alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But... How can we be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:55.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）そ…\Nでも どうやって確認すんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのレーダーみたいなやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that radar-like thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! He should have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:01.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ こいつが持ってたはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！ ダメだ　壊れてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかして これか？\N（加藤）持ってるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you talking about this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）\Nやっぱり そうだ　まだ１匹いる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only\NWhat the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉）一体 どうなってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinji's head got blown off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:21.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉）欣二 頭飛んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もしてねえのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he didn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And he didn't even come across\Nthat fuckin' alien or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:27.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とか星人に\N出会ってもいねえのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鉄男）マジかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't go back\Nuntil we get the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１匹捕まえねえと\N帰れないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたくない…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:44.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早くしてくれ… ガンツ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gantz...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加藤\N（加藤）計ちゃん どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His neck is broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ 首… 折れてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）寒い… 寒い…\N（岸本）寒いの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold... I'm cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My neck is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,首… なくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感覚ねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the second time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）２度目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前に１回　俺 首１回…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I... My neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I... My neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 首…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:16.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西丈一郎(じょういちろう)　中２　転落死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Joichiro Nishi, eight grader. I fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,転落死って…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,On my own... My neck... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:24.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分で首… 自分で…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... You mean you also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:41.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岸本）あなたも…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna die... This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤバイ もうすぐ死ぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to... die so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）早く… 死にたくない…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤダ　死ぬのイヤだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up yet! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ諦めないで！ お願い！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単に 死ぬなんて言わないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（計）岸本… そっか\Nお前 いちばん そう思うよな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... You must understand\Nhow he feels more than anybody else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I never...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）誰も…\N（計）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）嫌いじゃなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hated anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated... society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:24.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌いなの 世の中…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって メチャクチャじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's all messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I always felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）いっつも思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that I need to stay on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺だけは ちゃんとしないとって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all fucked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）メチャクチャなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't stay on track...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:50.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\Nちゃんと できなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:00.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）ヤダ… 死ぬのイヤだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤダ　ママ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）ママ… 謝らないと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ママ ごめん…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I tried hard but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:16.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ママ 一生懸命…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ママ ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）こ… 怖いよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, Mom... I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アア… 寒い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:40.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ママ 死んじゃうよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉）おい 答えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way we can be free from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らが自由になる方法あんのかよ？\N（鉄男）黙れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえのことばっか考えてねえで\Nこれ よく見とけ　見とけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so goddamn selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look at this! Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ママ 100点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,100 points...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（西）点数…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My score...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had 90 points...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:07.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,90点集まってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 10 more and I would have been free...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと10点で…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由になれたのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（加藤）死んだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedestrians and\NBicyclists only
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We all start out as pure and innocent babes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you taste the bitter fruit,\Ndon't be discouraged, walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's in the past, but the rain still stings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely as floating ice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I kiss your thin finger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And remember you crying
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this is the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget your last kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget his kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably think we're idiots, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春哉）てめえら\N俺のことバカだと思ってんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:38.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぜ 別に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no big deal, but listen.\NI'm running things around here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:42.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けどな 今この場 仕切ってんの\N俺なんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna get shot, Tetsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:45.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,撃たれてえのかよ？ ああ？ 鉄男！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Kato, You Wait Here"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回 “加藤くんは待っていて”
